Beijing Long-distance Call Building is the biggest hub of international and domestic long-distance calls. In addition to the wire communication system with large capacity, there is also modern wireless communication system - microware repeater system. This system can not only transmit thousands of calls simultaneously, but also transmit color TV signal, various signals of fax, telegram and images. Beijing Long-distance Call Building is the center of national microware repeater network for communication.
 








                                                                                                                                                                                                                      